<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <title>Login Notification</title>
  <style>
    body {
      font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
      background-color: #f4f6f8;
      margin: 0;
      padding: 0;
      color: #333;
    }
    .container {
      width: 90%;
      max-width: 600px;
      margin: 0 auto;
      background-color: #fff;
      border-radius: 8px;
      overflow: hidden;
      box-shadow: 0 2px 8px rgba(0,0,0,0.05);
    }
    .header {
      background-color: #0049b7;
      color: #fff;
      padding: 20px;
      text-align: center;
    }
    .logo {
      max-height: 50px;
      margin-bottom: 10px;
    }
    .content {
      padding: 30px;
    }
    .footer {
      padding: 20px;
      text-align: center;
      font-size: 12px;
      color: #999;
    }
    .btn {
      display: inline-block;
      margin-top: 20px;
      padding: 12px 20px;
      background-color: #0049b7;
      color: white;
      text-decoration: none;
      border-radius: 4px;
    }
    .info-block {
      background: #f1f1f1;
      padding: 15px;
      border-radius: 6px;
      margin-top: 15px;
      font-size: 14px;
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="container">
    <div class="header">
      <% if (logo) { %>
        <img src="<%= logo %>" alt="<%= site_name %> Logo" class="logo" />
      <% } %>
      <h2><%= site_name %> Login Notification</h2>
    </div>
    <div class="content">
      <p>Hi <strong><%= user.name %></strong>,</p>
      <p>This is to notify you that a login to your account was just made.</p>

      <div class="info-block">
        <p><strong>Email:</strong> <%= user.email %></p>
        <p><strong>Time:</strong> <%= new Date().toLocaleString('en-US', { timeZone: 'UTC' }) %> UTC</p>
        <p><strong>IP Address:</strong> <%= ip_address || 'Not provided' %></p>
        <p><strong>Device:</strong> <%= device_info || 'Unknown' %></p>
      </div>

      <p>If this was you, you can safely ignore this message.</p>
      <p>If you didnâ€™t log in, we strongly recommend resetting your password immediately.</p>

      <a href="<%= web_url %>/auth/reset-password" class="btn">Reset Password</a>
    </div>
    <div class="footer">
      &copy; <%= new Date().getFullYear() %> <%= site_name %>. All rights reserved. <br />
      Need help? Contact us at <%= contact_email %>.
    </div>
  </div>
</body>
</html>
